AutoMap==============	Pan Down									Down Arrow	Pan Up										Up Arrow	Pan Right									Right Arrow	Pan Left									Left Arrow	Zoom In										=	Zoom Out									-	Start/End Key							Tab	Go Big Key								0	Follow Key Toggle					F	Grid Key Toggle						G	Mark Key									M	Clear Mark Key						CHeads-Up==============	Green											Option + G	Indigo										Option + I	Brown											Option + B	Red												Option + R	Menus==============	Escape										EscapeText Entry==============	All unchanged							As Is	Backspace									BackspaceChat Macros==============	0													Option + 0	1													Option + 1	2													Option + 2	3													Option + 3	4													Option + 4	5													Option + 5	6													Option + 6	7													Option + 7	8													Option + 8	9													Option + 9Weapons==============	Hands/Chainsaw						1	Pistol										2	Shotgun/Combat Shotgun		3	Chain Gun									4	Missile Launcher					5	Plasma Gun								6	BFG9000										7	Chainsaw									8Movement & Actions==============	ADJUSTABLE:	Forward										Up Arrow / I / 8 on keypad	Backward									Down Arrow / K / 5 on keypad	Rotate Left								Left Arrow / J / 4 on keypad (Always strafe off if arrow keys)	Rotate Right							Right Arrow / L / 6 on keypad (Always strafe off if arrow keys)	Strafe Left								Left Arrow + Always Strafe On / U / 7 on keypad	Strafe Right							Right Arrow + Always Strafe On / O / 9 on keypad	Strafe										Control	Run												Shift	Fire Weapon								D	Use (Action)							Space	NON-ADJUSTABLE:		Pause											N/A - Menu Only	Message Refresh						Return	Talk											T	Other==============	Screen size down					-	Screen size up						+	F1												Help	F2												Save As	F3												Load	F4												Sound Volume	F5												Detail toggle	F6												QuickSave	F7												End Game	F8												Toggle Messages	F9												QuickLoad	F10												QuickDoom	F11												Gamma ToggleMenu Keyboard Equivalents==============	New Game									Command + N	Open Saved Game						Command + O	Quickload									Command + 9	End Game									Command + 7	Save Game									Command + S	Quit											Command + Q		Undo											Command + Z	Cut												Command + X	Copy											Command + C	Paste											Command + V		Keyboard									Command + K	Mouse											Command + M	Joystick									Command + J		Movement									Command + T	Help											Command + 1	Sound Volume							Command + 4	Graphic Detail						Command + 5	Toggle Messages						Command + 8	Next Viewpoint						Command + 2	Pause											Command + P			